{
  "stem": "8.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We weren't taken to any shelter or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And as we we're lining up for lunch after the air raid, a tall man came by.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I don't know if he was a prisoner or he was a guard or he was a-- I don't know what he was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He gave me at big container of soup, just selected me out out of thousands of people and just gave me a container of soup.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I-- I wasn't-- I couldn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As I said, maybe because I looked so young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "At other times, I developed a skill to work with files, which were our tools, to make little charms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Just when I was very bored and when I had a little time, I-- I made those out of-- for my own fun.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And one day, a German officer saw that and started yelling at me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But at the end, he said, I want that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I want to send it home for my kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then he gave me an order.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Every day, I was to produce more and more of these things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then other people asked me to do them, and I got a little extra food here and there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So these things helped me to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "One day, our group, about 26 people, were asked to leave this big hall and go and work in a smaller place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This was like a little island of-- of tranquility for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were not supervised anymore by these very vicious German officers, but by a civilian man, a German civilian man, who was kind, who was strict but kind.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And one day-- I think my story sounds like I was always given something, but I guess it was true.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "One day, he gave me an apple.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
